page.title: 20 PARISH NOTICES Cont...
page.content:
The Rockhampton Summer Fete will be on Sat July 27th on the Cricket Field. To be opened by Mr. John Cope our local MP Various stalls,games of skill,grand draw,fancy dress,ice cream and other refreshments.Don't forget the evening carnival and barbeque etc.See posters for details of the weeks activities and join in when you can. Church Notices - All services will be at 9.30 a.m.on Sunday's in July. 7th - Rev.W.Burlton. 14th - Rev.Canon K.Preston. 21st and 28th - the Vicar. The Parochial Church Council will meet on Weds.10th July at 7.30 pm.
Contributors to the survey. I Monkton, M.Barber, L.Shaw, B.Pritchard, P.Wood, C.Alexander, M.Simmons, D.Simmons, A. James, S.Mehra, D.Webb, R.Travell, T. Watkins, J.Hatteea, B.Ward, J.Morrissey C.Taylor, P.Simmons, P.Shorney and Prep
